
# Summary: 50 chars maximum. That's here --------|


# Body: Explain what and why, wrap at 72 characters. That's here ------|

# Best practices for commit messages:
#   1. Limit the subject line to 50 characters
#   2. Capitalize the subject line, no period at end
#   3. Separate subject from body with a blank line
#   4. Use the imperative mood in the subject line
#   5. Wrap the body at 72 characters
#   6. Explain:
#      i.   Why the changes were needed.
#      ii.  Why the changes were made.
#      iii. What effect the changes have.
#   7. Refer to the issue # if in response to one
